'''迪拜航空981号班机'''是[[迪拜航空|迪拜航空]]一架从[[阿联酋|阿联酋]][[迪拜|迪拜]]飞往[[俄罗斯|俄罗斯]][[顿河畔罗斯托夫|顿河畔罗斯托夫]]的[[波音737新世代|波音737-800]]客机。2016年3月19日在俄罗斯境内顿河畔罗斯托夫机场降落时坠毁。机上有55名乘客，7名机组成员，共62人，全部遇难。<ref>{{cite news|url=http://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/18/europe/russia-plane-crash/index.html|title=Airliner crashes in Russia; 62 aboard reported dead|publisher=CNN|date=2016-03-19|accessdate=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319021955/http://edition.cnn.com/2016/03/18/europe/russia-plane-crash/index.html|dead-url=no}}</ref>飞机试图降落时第一次因風切變而復飛，然后做等待盘旋超过1小时，第二次復飛时发生了事故。

==事故经过==
981航班在莫斯科时间1:41 (UTC+3)在罗斯托夫机场第一次尝试着陆因機載氣象雷達檢測到風切變而[[复飞|复飞]]。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://info.flightmapper.net/flight/flydubai_FZ_981?date=2016-3-18 |title=flydubai flight FZ 981: Dubai - Rostov |website=FlightMapper |access-date=2016-03-19 |archive-date=2016-03-27 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160327202122/http://info.flightmapper.net/flight/flydubai_FZ_981?date=2016-3-18 |dead-url=no }}</ref>随后在机场的[[等待航线|等待航线]]持续盘旋了近2个小时。<ref name="Aviation Herald">{{cite web|last1=Hradecky|first1=Simon|title=Crash: Flydubai B738 at Rostov on Don on Mar 19th 2016, struck wing onto runway after holding for 2 hours|url=http://avherald.com/h?article=495997e2|website=Aviation Herald|accessdate=2016-03-19|date=2015-03-19|archive-date=2017-10-14|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171014203344/http://avherald.com/h?article=495997e2|dead-url=no}}</ref><ref name="FR24 track">{{cite web|title=Playback of FlyDubai flight FZ981|url=https://www.flightradar24.com/data/aircraft/a6-fdn/#922b3bd|website=Flightradar24|accessdate=2016-03-19|archive-date=2019-04-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190422054210/https://www.flightradar24.com/data/aircraft/a6-fdn/#922b3bd|dead-url=no}}</ref>在981航班的第一次与第二次着陆尝试之间，[[俄航|俄航]]的莫斯科-罗斯托夫航线的1166号航班曾3次着陆失败而备降{{tsl|en|Krasnodar International Airport|克拉斯诺达尔国际机场}}。<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://mobile.twitter.com/flightradar24/status/711068277779402752?ref_src=twsrc%255Egoogle%257Ctwcamp%255Eserp%257Ctwgr%255Etweet|title=Flightradar24|website=Twitter.com/Flightradar24|access-date=2016-03-19}}</ref>981航班第二次复飞过程中坠毁在22号跑道附近。

根据[[空中交通管制|空中交通管制]]（ATC）的地空通话实况录音，981航班的飛行員在尚未建立{{tsl|en|Instrument landing system localizer|仪表降落系统信标}}（飞行员不靠目视而是使用仪表降落系统指示跑道中心线）時向ATC报告需要爬升到飞行空層80 (FL80)—即{{convert|8000|ft|sigfig=2}}以便可能的再次复飞。{{efn|name=Flight level|Aircraft altitude is measured by air pressure, which [[Atmospheric_pressure#Altitude_variation|declines]] as altitude above sea level increases. A [[flight_level|flight level]] is the [[pressure_altitude|pressure altitude]] in hundreds of feet.}} 之后，飞行员报告已经建立仪表降落系统信标并将下降飞行高度。<ref name="youtube.com">{{cite av media|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=57v4_U-N15c&feature=youtu.be|title=FlyDubai 981 Crash ATC Communications|date=2016-03-18|publisher=|accessdate=2016-03-19|via=YouTube|archive-date=2017-03-08|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20170308084439/https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=57v4_U-N15c&feature=youtu.be|dead-url=no}}</ref> 在距离跑道端{{convert|5.5|km}}处，飞机在1500英尺高度，开始了再次爬升。在爬升至{{convert|4050|ft|abbr=on}}<!-- source below, flightradar twitter -->時, 飞机開始以超过21,000英尺/分钟的速率陡然下降<ref>{{cite web|url=https://twitter.com/flightradar24/status/711087904366456832|title=Flightradar24 on Twitter|work=Twitter|accessdate=2016-03-19|archive-date=2017-10-24|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20171024182454/https://twitter.com/flightradar24/status/711087904366456832|dead-url=no}}</ref>并在约1分钟后，当地时间03:42撞地坠毁。<ref>{{cite web|url=https://www.flightradar24.com/data/flights/fz981/#922b3bd|title=FlyDubai flight FZ981 - Flightradar24|publisher=|accessdate=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-20|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160320145412/https://www.flightradar24.com/data/flights/fz981#922b3bd|dead-url=no}}</ref>坠毁前，飞行员显然再次复飞，向ATC报告："Going around, Skydubai{{efn|Skydubai是该航班的[[呼号|呼号]]。}} 981"。 ATC告知981航班切换到另外的空中交通管制："Skydubai 981, contact Rostov Radar on 121.2"。 981航班确认了这一情况："121.2, bye-bye", 这也是最后一次通话。<ref name="youtube.com"/>

根据官方报告，飞机坠毁在跑道左侧{{convert|253|m}}处。<ref>{{Cite web |url=https://meduza.io/feature/2016/03/19/krushenie-boinga-v-rostove |title=存档副本 |accessdate=2016-03-19 |archive-date=2016-03-29 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160329114858/https://meduza.io/feature/2016/03/19/krushenie-boinga-v-rostove |dead-url=no }}</ref>并且完全解体。<ref name="RT live updates">{{cite news|title=Flydubai flight FZ981 crash live updates|url=https://www.rt.com/news/336194-flydubai-fz981-crash-rostov/|accessdate=2016-03-19|work=RT|date=2016-03-19|quote=3:42 GMT: “The plane completely disintegrated at the very beginning of the runway,” the local Emergencies Ministry chief, Igor Oder, said during a conference call held by the head of the Ministry, TASS reports.|archive-date=2016-03-19|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160319040705/https://www.rt.com/news/336194-flydubai-fz981-crash-rostov/|dead-url=no}}</ref>俄联邦紧急情况部称飞机机翼先撞击地面。<ref>{{cite web|title=Уточненная информация об аварии с самолетом в г.Ростове-н/Д|trans-title=Updated information about the accident to the aircraft in Rostov-N/A|url=http://61.mchs.gov.ru/operationalpage/operational/item/3515193/|publisher=Russian Ministry of Emergency Situations|accessdate=2016-03-19|language=ru|date=2016-03-19|archive-date=2016-03-22|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160322051745/http://61.mchs.gov.ru/operationalpage/operational/item/3515193|dead-url=yes}}</ref>视频监控显示飞机陡然下降撞击地面。<ref>BNO News  https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OB0m4Z92418 {{Wayback|url=https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=OB0m4Z92418 |date=20170310235303 }}</ref> 
根据机场救援人员提供的消息，现场残骸的散布情况显示，飞机触地时，速度达到400km/h，俯角约为60度，就连机上最坚固的部件--镁合金制成的轮圈都被摧毁了。<ref name="TASS">{{cite news|url=http://tass.ru/proisshestviya/2756242|title=Источник: Boeing потерпел крушение, пытаясь уйти на третий круг|date=2016-03-19|agency=[[Russian_News_Agency_TASS|TASS]]|language=ru|trans-title=Source: Boeing crashed, trying to go around for a third attempt|accessdate=2016-03-20|archive-date=2016-03-21|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160321080726/http://tass.ru/proisshestviya/2756242|dead-url=no}}</ref> 他们的估计与Flightradar24上的数据基本相符。<ref name="Meduza 20 Mar">{{cite news |url=https://meduza.io/feature/2016/03/20/krushenie-boinga-flydubai-chto-do-sih-por-neizvestno |title=Крушение «Боинга» Flydubai. Что до сих пор неизвестно |trans-title=Crash of Flydubai's Boeing. What is still unknown |work=[[Meduza|Meduza]] |date=2016-03-20 |accessdate=2016-03-20 |language=ru |archive-date=2016-04-01 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160401234651/https://meduza.io/feature/2016/03/20/krushenie-boinga-flydubai-chto-do-sih-por-neizvestno |dead-url=no }}</ref> <ref name="TASS"/>
